{"tid":1780764,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"4個月大狗仔轉糧","createTime":"2019-12-12T15:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T06:41:02.000Z","uid":104424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"97f406a0539a1b1818c47900e1629b3d960cd018","tid":1780764,"uid":104424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"有冇人知Brabanconne呢隻牌子好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上網搵過好似冇乜評價<br />\n<br />\n另外巴打絲打仲有冇狗糧推薦，上網搵過呢幾個牌子都有人讚:<br />\n<br />\n1. Orijen<br />\n2. Fromm<br />\n3. Canidae<br />\n4. Wellness <br />\n<br />\n但我知唔係話貴就好，我隻狗狗氣管好似係差少少，有冇話邊種啱佢啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b462889a359c14c38fe98a9fdf50c5261267c5a","tid":1780764,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:52:44.000Z","msg":"借po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發動世界級遊行！Who stand with us世界巡遊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1780766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1780766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"082008c1c0cdd2edde2bce5d6a4ad57abb5e27b3","tid":1780764,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:19:10.000Z","msg":"我隻狗早排轉咗食Acana<br />\n暫時係最滿意嘅狗糧<br />\n狗狗又肯食 亦無話食幾次就厭<br />\n而且啲便便都幾靚<br />\n唯獨啲狗糧有啲大粒<br />\n初初都擔心隻狗唔咬就吞"},{"pid":"297fe4c8fbd85c3c300d34b887a3fc92a104d93d","tid":1780764,"uid":121087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"orijen 同acana都好<br />\n<br />\nwellness 就睇邊條line<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://moesonson.com/狗糧評價/acana-singles-愛肯拿單一\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoesonson.com%2F%E7%8B%97%E7%B3%A7%E8%A9%95%E5%83%B9%2Facana-singles-%E6%84%9B%E8%82%AF%E6%8B%BF%E5%96%AE%E4%B8%80&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=939cf64e\" data-auto-link t